<!-- to update these nuget packages, change them in <SolutionDir>\SharedItems.props file,
	then search the "*.*proj *.config *.props" files in the C:\Users\pete_\source\repos\encoding-converters-core
	in Notepad++ for the version numbers (e.g. 10.0.7)
	and update them to match the versions in SharedItems.props.

	Then with VS closed, in an admin dev command prompt window, navigate to the solution directory and run:
	git clean -fxd

	dir /s project.assets.json	# to make sure these are all gone.

	then:

	dotnet restore
-->
<!--Include this in any exe that uses EncConverters core to make sure you have the references needed for any and all converter types-->
